139
00:07:26,030 --> 00:07:28,752
in terms of candidate, a good culture fit for the studio.

140
00:07:29,513 --> 00:07:33,794
And then we'll typically request to hop on with the hiring manager.

141
00:07:33,854 --> 00:07:36,535
That way we can really dig in and know who we're going

142
00:07:36,555 --> 00:07:38,835
to be submitting candidates directly to.

143
00:07:40,556 --> 00:07:42,797
And have that relationship going.

144
00:07:42,837 --> 00:07:44,537
