151
00:08:01,762 --> 00:08:03,744
At the beginning of the process.

152
00:08:04,464 --> 00:08:07,667
Really work together to have an effective recruiting strategy.

153
00:08:08,508 --> 00:08:11,411
A recruiter really is a force multiplier to you.

154
00:08:11,711 --> 00:08:14,313
And so really it's just work together in tandem to understand what it is.

155
00:08:14,373 --> 00:08:18,016
And so the hiring managers have a clear expectation for the studio's hiring needs.

156
00:08:18,897 --> 00:08:22,961
And work to have keywords or anything that will help them on their search on LinkedIn

157
00:08:23,061 --> 00:08:24,222
or any sourcing they can have.

158
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:30,925
I always like to make sure I nail down very specifically.

159
00:08:30,945 --> 00:08:34,610
I like to, when I talk to our clients or the hiring managers,

