I always like to have examples. I'm very visual, so if they can send me

164
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:48,941
a portfolio from their team so I can get an idea of the style

165
00:08:49,301 --> 00:08:53,162
or a video that I can really focus on, that way I can

166
00:08:53,262 --> 00:08:55,703
narrow the aperture when it comes to helping them,

167
00:08:56,723 --> 00:08:59,224
helping us find them the type of candidate they want.

