185
00:10:10,752 --> 00:10:14,993
So those are really the two biggest ones that I'm hearing right now.

186
00:10:16,265 --> 00:10:19,586
Yeah, for us, remote is huge after COVID.

187
00:10:19,626 --> 00:10:22,647
The last two years, most people have gotten comfortable working from home.

188
00:10:23,267 --> 00:10:24,947
Most people can do their jobs from home.

189
00:10:24,967 --> 00:10:27,248
So a lot of people are currently looking for that.

190
00:10:28,868 --> 00:10:31,369
And then creative flexibility is another one.

191
00:10:31,589 --> 00:10:33,850
Growth opportunity is something we see a lot.

192
00:10:34,650 --> 00:10:39,031
We also definitely in this industry, work life balance is huge.

193
00:10:39,711 --> 00:10:44,874
no more crunch. I don't think I think most studios aren't doing it anymore. So, you know,

194
00:10:44,914 --> 00:10:52,658
people are excited about that. But each candidate is very unique. So I usually try to do my,

195
00:10:53,598 --> 00:10:58,361
